## E Color Diamond Price Per Carat (2026 Data)

As of 2026, natural diamond prices have softened. A high-quality 1-carat natural E-color diamond costs between **$4,000 and $7,800**.

A comparable D-color ranges from **$4,300 to $8,800**. You pay a **15% to 25% premium** for a D-grade that you physically cannot see without laboratory equipment.

